comments: Redick (NOP) makes marginal contact with James (LAL) before James gathers and makes the pass.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the floor of Pelicans possession is overturned to Lakers possession.  The ball is last touched by Williams (NOP) before going out of bounds.
James (LAL) makes a natural move during his drive to the basket as he releases from contact with Holiday (NOP).
As Holiday (NOP) swipes down in an attempt to block the shot, he does not make contact with James's (LAL) arm.
As Ingram (NOP) swipes at the ball in an attempt to block James's (LAL) putback shot attempt, he avoids making contact with James's arm.

Replay review of the foul called on Caldwell-Pope (LAL) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed unsuccessful.  Caldwell-Pope makes contact to Ingram's elbow during the start of his upward shooting motion that affects his jump shot attempt.

Holiday (NOP) maintains a legal defensive position in the post as he has his left arm collapsed against his body and he absorbs the contact from James (LAL).  As James goes to pass the ball, Holiday does not make contact to his arm.
Davis (LAL) is in the paint for less than three seconds when the shot is imminent.
Caruso (LAL) maintains a legal guarding position during the jump shot attempt by Ingram (NOP).
James (LAL) makes clean contact with the ball when he swipes down in an attempt to dislodge it from Hart (NOP).
Kuzma (LAL) makes contact to Hart's (NOP) arm and affects his SQBR.
Holiday (NOP) maintains a legal guarding position on James (LAL) in the post and then makes clean contact with the ball.
Davis (LAL) briefly places an arm to the front of Ingram (NOP), but the contact is marginal.  He moves alongside Ingram's path and then makes clean contact with the ball.

James (LAL) moves alongside of Ingram (NOP) with his left forearm legally collapsed against his body.  He keeps his right arm vertical and does not deliver any contact to Ingram as he loses control of the ball.

After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the floor of Pelicans possession is confirmed.  The ball does not go off of Ingram's (NOP) knee and James (LAL) is the last player to make contact with it before it goes out of bounds.
Caruso (LAL) maintains a legal guarding position during the jump shot attempt by Redick (NOP).
Hart (NOP) commits a take foul on Davis (LAL).
Williams (NOP) commits a take foul on Davis (LAL).
Davis (LAL) cleanly steals the throw-in intended for Ingram (NOP).
Ingram (NOP) grabs Davis (LAL) after the steal and affects his SQBR.  After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the floor of a common foul is confirmed.
Davis (LAL) maintains a legal guarding position during the jump shot attempt by Ingram (NOP).
